  <h2>Options</h2>

  <h3>Disabled and active states</h3>
  <p>Links are customizable for different circumstances. Use <code>.disabled</code> for unclickable links and <code>.active</code> to indicate the current page.</p>
  <div class="bs-docs-example">
    <div class="pagination pagination-centered">
      <ul>
        <li class="disabled"><a href="#">&laquo;</a></li>
        <li class="active"><a href="#">1</a></li>
        <li><a href="#">2</a></li>
        <li><a href="#">3</a></li>
        <li><a href="#">4</a></li>
        <li><a href="#">5</a></li>
        <li><a href="#">&raquo;</a></li>
     </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
<div class="tab-content">
<pre class="prettyprint linenums tab-pane fade in active" id="pagination-disabled-active-haml">
.pagination
  %ul
    %li.disabled
      %a{:href => "#"} Prev
    %li.active
      %a{:href => "#"} 1
    Lorem
</pre>
<pre class="prettyprint linenums tab-pane fade" id="pagination-disabled-active-html">
&lt;div class="pagination"&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li class="disabled"&gt;&lt;a href="#"&gt;Prev&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class="active"&gt;&lt;a href="#"&gt;1&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
Lorem
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
</pre>
</div>
<ul class="nav nav-pills example-types">
  <li class="active"><a href="#pagination-disabled-active-haml" data-toggle="tab">HAML</a></li>
  <li><a href="#pagination-disabled-active-html" data-toggle="tab">HTML</a></li>
</ul>

  <p>You can optionally swap out active or disabled anchors for spans to remove click functionality while retaining intended styles.</p>
<div class="tab-content">
<pre class="prettyprint linenums tab-pane fade in active" id="pagination-span-swap-haml">
.pagination
  %ul
